- "seeds" metaphorically refers to pieces of content;
- "sprouted" indicates published content;
- "gardeners" are the users who access the content;
- "watered" means accessed or viewed the content.

- 'a dozen' typically refers to 12 units;
- 'in the last year' refers to the calendar year 2023, given the current year is 2024;
- 'produced' and 'published' both refer to the act of putting out content.

